## How to think about mobile vs web

| Web | Mobile |
|-----|--------|
| Marketing landing (`/`) | Usually **not** in the store app — use website or a light **Welcome** screen |
| Sidebar navigation | **Bottom navigation** (4–5 tabs) + stacks for detail flows |
| Dialogs (receipt, add product) | Often **full screens** or bottom sheets |
| Dense tables | **Lists** + tap → **detail** screens |

