## 5. Motion & interaction (iOS 26 “feel” in Flutter)

| Interaction | Spec suggestion |
|-------------|-----------------|
| Page push | 300–350ms, easeOutCubic; iOS parallax optional |
| Bottom sheet | Spring open; drag dismiss; glass header strip |
| Add to cart | Brief scale + haptic (light); badge bounce |
| Pay success | Confetti **off** by default; clear checkmark + haptic success |
| Tab switch | Cross-fade or shared axis; POS tab no heavy animation |
| Pull to refresh | Both platforms on lists |
| Error shake | Subtle on invalid PIN / failed M-Pesa |

Use **`flutter_animate`** or built-in `AnimationController` with **one motion token file** (durations/easing) shared across platforms.

**Haptics:** Light on add-to-cart; medium on payment success; heavy on void/refund confirm.

