## 6. Android parity (not a second-class UI)

| iOS 26 pattern | Android equivalent |
|----------------|-------------------|
| Liquid Glass bar | M3 **surface container** + blur on Android 12+ (`RenderEffect`) |
| Collapsing header | `NestedScrollView` + `LargeTopAppBar` |
| Sheets | Modal bottom sheet, rounded top `radius-xl` |
| In-place alert | Snackbar or anchored dialog |
| Dynamic Island | Skip; use status banner for M-Pesa pending |

**Material You dynamic color:** **Off by default** so teal/purple doesn’t break UzaPoint neutrals. Optional “use wallpaper colors” in settings v2 for consumer-facing apps only — **not recommended for POS**.

