## 9. Tablet vs phone

| Device | Navigation | iOS 26 notes |
|--------|------------|--------------|
| Phone | Bottom tabs | Collapsing glass bar |
| Tablet | Optional **navigation rail** + POS split view (products | cart) | Glass rail; POS two-pane like web layout |

Tablet POS can mirror **web POS** layout while phone keeps stacked flows — **same tokens**, different layout breakpoints.

