## 10. What not to do

- Full Liquid Glass on checkout totals or barcode overlay.  
- Different primary color on mobile (e.g. blue) vs web black — breaks brand.  
- iOS-only features with no Android fallback (live activities, etc.) in v1.  
- Heavy animations before M-Pesa callback returns.  
- Tiny touch targets on POS (min **48dp**; prefer 56 for cart qty).  
- Custom fonts that don’t support **KES** and numerals tabular lining for amounts.

